title: Static Analysis

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to access the list of accounts known by the phone.

android.permission.AUTHENTICATE_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to use the account authenticator capabilities of the Account Manager, including creating accounts as well as obtaining and setting their passwords.

android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to perform operations like adding and removing accounts and deleting their password.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.GET_TASKS.description: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

com.campmobile.android.moot.permission.C.description: Allows the application to receive push notifications.

com.huawei.android.launcher.permission.W.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

com.oppo.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTI.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

manifest_analysis.desc: The Network Security Configuration feature lets apps customize their network security settings in a safe, declarative configuration file without modifying app code. These settings can be configured for specific domains and for a specific app.
manifest_analysis.name: App has a Network Security Configuration [android:networkSecurityConfig]

manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.campmobile.android.moot.ActionSendActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.

"shop_home_desc" : "Chào mừng bạn đến với Cửa hàng Xu Moot!
Các vật phẩm mới xuất hiện ở đây hàng ngày khi hết thời gian. Vì thế đừng rời mắt.
Nhấn vào mỗi vật phẩm để xem thêm thông tin và xem nó có đáng giá bằng xu quý giá của bạn không!
Bạn cần thêm Xu Moot? Hãy kiểm tra các cách để kiếm thêm xu bằng việc nhấn vào nút "Mục tiêu" phía dưới.
Ở phía trên màn hình, thời gian còn lại để mua vật phẩm sẽ được hiển thị. Tất cả vật phẩm sẽ được thay thế khi hết thời gian, vì thế hãy mua kịp thời!
Vật phẩm đã mua không thể đổi hoặc hoàn trả. Xu có thể bị mất đi sau khi mua vì xóa bài đăng hoặc các lý do khác.
Chúc bạn mua sắm vui vẻ!"

Nous espérons que vous profiterez de vos emplettes !"

Umarım aışverişten hoşlanırsın!"

¡Esperamos que disfrute comprando!"

"shop_home_desc" : "Добро пожаловать в Магазин монет Moot!

Купленные предметы нельзя поменять или вернуть. Монеты могут быть отобраны назад после покупки за удаление поста или по другим причинам.

playstore_details.title: Moot - LFG & Gaming Discussion
playstore_details.description:
Moot is the premier app for anybody that plays video games. Moot is a community platform dedicated to streamlining the Looking for Group process, as well as sharing up-to-date news, spicy memes, helpful guides, and more about today’s most popular games. 

● Find your teammates with our LFG feature.
● Stay up-to-date on the latest reviews, highlights, and trending memes.
● Communicate privately with your friends using our Direct Message feature.
● Buy fresh items and spice up your profile with your Moot Coins.
● Follow Moot’s top content creators and get updates when they post.
● Level up by sharing, voting, and discussing the games you enjoy playing.
● Decide if content is up to your standard through upvoting or downvoting.
● Fight boredom – navigate through different lounges and check out what’s trending among the community.
● Over a dozen lounges opened: Fortnite, Apex Legends, Call of Duty, Red Dead Redemption, Rainbow Six Siege, PUBG, GTA, Overwatch, Clash Royale, Battlefield, and more!
● Also available on PC at moot.us

With moot, we want to grow with and for the community. Let’s make it happen!
Have questions, problems, or feedback? Reach out to us at 
moot_help@navercorp.com
